What:		/sys/devices/platform/gdmc_dhub/uart_mux
Date:		January 2024
KernelVersion:	6.1.57-android14-11
Description:
		Query or set the UART Muliplexer setting managed by the Google
		GDMC (Google Debug Management Controller) DHUB (Debug Hub).

		The value is the identifier for one of the platform's
		subsystem UART ports.   The definition of subsystem UART
		identifiers is platform specific.

What:		/sys/devices/platform/gdmc_dhub/baudrate
Date:		January 2024
KernelVersion:	6.1.57-android14-11
Description:
		Query or set the baudrate for the UART interface provided by the DHUB
		over the device debug USB port SBU lines.  The SBU lines carry a
		data stream consisting of virtualized subsystem	UARTs multiplexed with
		other debug packets.

